item.title: PicoCTF Part 1
item.description: Recently, I started participating in many CTFs and wanted to hone my CTF skills. That’s where I came across PicoCTF. It’s a page where they collated all the CTF challenges they used for their events (with over 200 challenges). This is part 1 of my PicoCTF series where I walk through every PicoCTF challenge (there are more than 200 challenges collated).
